<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">ب ر ن:</span> <span class="c2">(الْبَرْنِيُّ)</span> ضَرْبٌ مِنَ التَّمْرِ وَ <span class="c2">(الْبَرْنِيَّةُ)</span> إِنَاءٌ مِنْ خَزَفٍ. وَ <span class="c2">(يَبْرِينُ)</span> مَوْضِعٌ يُقَالُ: رَمْلُ يَبْرِينَ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>